{"tid":782494,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"少壯不努力，讀u徒傷悲","createTime":"2018-08-16T19:12:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T21:17:33.000Z","uid":160998,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"830691c4a4b7e4450ccdd8e1a2ee82493db33231","tid":782494,"uid":160998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T19:12:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細個英文好差，又無太努力去惡補英文<br />\n好彩考到個level 3，其實入到u根本係廢，又要讀補底又剩。<br />\n社會對於英文真係好重視<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以想請教各位fg最少50k，讀各神科既連登巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有無咩英文練習或者書係適合好似我得level3既人睇去惡補下考到個ielts 6.5都好</span><br />\n<br />\n各位未考dse既真係要努力讀英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 考完dse入到u既各位都要繼續好好繼續進修英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係好後悔無出200%努力去讀英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe1f71f59ad32eb8764b658b45345d1d8add4cb1","tid":782494,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T19:15:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8294aafe039f7ea27c13f158325f13849ef7b7e6","tid":782494,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T19:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9ca1e23c0054e9587b1add95a198612c91a2a4","tid":7824